OL,3,CMan first to be jailed following
OL,4,Cwidespread rioting
OL,6,FA teenager has become what is thought
OL,7,Fto be the first person to receive a
OL,8,Fprison sentence after riots broke out
OL,9,Facross the country in relation to the
OL,10,FSouthport killings.
OL,12,FJames Nelson, 18, donned a pink
OL,13,Fbalaclava in a bid to 'evade
OL,14,Fidentification' after damaging two
OL,15,Fpolice cars after violence erupted in
OL,16,FBolton town centre.
OL,18,FBut, he was jailed for two months
OL,19,Fafter pleading guilty to causing
OL,20,Fcriminal damage during rioting on
OL,21,FSunday 4 August.
