OL,3,CMan first to be jailed following
OL,4,Cwidespread rioting
OL,6,FJohn Potter, prosecuting, told
OL,7,FManchester Magistrates Court that two
OL,8,Fpolice cars, a Ford Focus and a
OL,9,FPeugeot, were parked in the Morrisons
OL,10,Fcar park on Black Horse Street.
OL,12,FMr Potter said: "On the first vehicle,
OL,13,Fthere was significant damage to the
OL,14,Fwindscreen, the side windows were
OL,15,Fsmashed and the driver's side wing
OL,16,Fmirror was also damaged.
OL,18,F"On the second vehicle, the back
OL,19,Fwindow was smashed and the near side
OL,20,Fwindow was smashed, with significant
OL,21,Fdamage to the front window."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
