OL,3,CMan first to be jailed following
OL,4,Cwidespread rioting
OL,6,FDozens of people have appeared in
OL,7,Fcourtrooms facing charges related to
OL,8,Fthe unrest which has now lasted a week
OL,9,Facross England and in parts of
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,FIt follows the deaths of Alice Dasilva
OL,13,FAguiar, nine, Bebe King, six, and
OL,14,FElsie Dot Stancombe, seven, who were
OL,15,Ffatally stabbed after a knifeman
OL,16,Fentered a dance class on Hart Street
OL,17,Fin Southport, on 29 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
