OL,3,CMan first to be jailed following
OL,4,Cwidespread rioting
OL,6,FEight young girls suffered knife
OL,7,Fwounds ` with five of them left in a
OL,8,Fcritical condition ` while two adults,
OL,9,FLeanne Lucas and John Hayes, were also
OL,10,Fcritically hurt.
OL,12,FApproximately 100 charges have been
OL,13,Flaid relating to the riots, Mr
OL,14,FParkinson said, as more than 400
OL,15,Fpeople have been arrested.
OL,17,FGabriella Black, mitigating, said
OL,18,FNelson suffers from ADHD and issues
OL,19,Fwith anger for which he was prescribed
OL,20,Fmedication that he had 'not been
OL,21,Ftaking'.
