OL,3,CMan first to be jailed following
OL,4,Cwidespread rioting
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Hirst said: "You
OL,7,Fattended that violence with the intent
OL,8,Fof causing trouble. You were involved
OL,9,Fin the appalling and shameful violent
OL,10,Fdisorder that impacted not just the
OL,11,Fnational community, but in particular
OL,12,Fthe Bolton community.
OL,14,F"I accept you may have difficulties
OL,15,Fbut I understand that everyone
OL,16,Finvolved in that violence has
OL,17,Fdifficulties."
OL,19,FShe added that an immediate custodial
OL,20,Fsentence would 'deter others from
OL,21,Fdamaging police vehicles'.
